element.name: Sign Of The Times by Donnacha, Traditional Cache (1/1.5)
element.long-description:
Located in the Glen Of The Downs in Co. Wicklow. Bring a pen to log your find.
The Glen was home to the "Eco Warriors" back in 1997. They were campaigning against the building of a dual carriageway which you will travel on, on the way to the cache site. For over 3 years the Eco Warriors lived in tunnels and trees in the Glen, but it all came to a head in Feb 2000 when 13 of the campaigners were sent to prison, and a couple months after, work got underway to build the road.
Visit the Geocaching Ireland discussion forum HERE
element.encoded-hints: Hope for some sort of sign to guide you
